{"type":null,"faqId":24738,"title":"荣耀 X2是否可以作为 Wi-Fi 热点？怎么操作？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>支持数据业务的荣耀 X2可以作为 Wi-Fi 热点。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如需使用Wi-Fi热点功能，请先开启荣耀 X2的数据开关。其他设备通过荣耀 X2共享的网络上网时，将使用荣耀 X2中 SIM 卡的数据流量。您可以参考如下步骤进行设置：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.6.5.2.3.1.1\"></a><span>在主屏幕上点击“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.6.5.2.3.2.1\"></a><span>在“无线和网络”区域，点击“更多... &gt; 移动网络共享 &gt; 便携式 Wi-Fi 热点”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"figd0e1494\"><a name=\"gen-id1.6.5.2.3.2.1.3.1\"></a></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=86140\" style=\"width:5.423611in;height:2.557639in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.6.5.2.3.3.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.6.5.2.3.3.1\"></a><span>点击或滑动热点名称后的开关至 “</span><a name=\"gen-id1.6.5.2.3.3.1.1.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.6.5.2.3.3.1.1.1\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=86141\" style=\"width:0.22847222in;height:0.16527778in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，开启便携式 Wi-Fi 热点。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"gen-id1.6.5.2.3.3.2\"><a name=\"figd0e1505\"><a name=\"gen-id1.6.5.2.3.3.2.1.1\"></a></a></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=86142\" style=\"width:1.7395834in;height:2.5583334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.6.5.2.3.4.1\"></a><span>点击“配置 Wi-Fi 热点”，然后根据界面显示配置您的无线局域网网络名称、密码等信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"figd0e1517\"><a name=\"gen-id1.6.5.2.4.1\"></a></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=86143\" style=\"width:3.5833333in;height:2.557639in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span>配置完成后，其他需要上网的无线设备可以搜索并连接至 荣耀 X2 提供的 Wi-Fi 热点。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<a name=\"gen-id1.6.5.2.6\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=86144\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":170,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8738","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Internet-Data-Sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1430104341000,"seriesProductName":"GEM-703L","visitedTimes":166,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"wifi 热点,热点,共享网络,网络共享","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}